  <summary>11/2/2005--Introduced.
Safe Drinking Water for All Act - Amends the Safe Drinking Water Act to: (1) revise requirements for drinking water studies relating to infants, children, women, and pregnant women to require an evaluation of the effect of contaminants on endocrine and other health functions; and (2) require such studies to be made available to the public.</summary>
